49 Megha-gaṇā na dṛśyante na viviktaḥ, 50 Na vidyullatā na Tāmasa-sutā, 51 Yā tatra deśāntaram bahuśaḥ karoti;
52 Śuṣkaḥ vāyuḥ na udeti adhikaḥ 53 Yat tri-śreṇyāḥ śikharaṃ yad ahaṃ abravam, 54 Yatra Paurava-pradhānaḥ pādayor nyāsau karoti.

